sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant API
    participant FS as Filesystem
    participant DB as SQLite

    User->>Frontend: Click folder
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/browse?path=/photos
    API->>FS: readdir() + stat()
    FS-->>API: File entries
    API->>DB: Query media metadata (if indexed)
    DB-->>API: width, height, duration
    API-->>Frontend: JSON response
    Frontend-->>User: Render table
